      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KEWPIE DOLL (3) jumped from a low draw and boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten 0.8 lengths (20.19) behind Precious Wonder at this track. Smart beginner who should take advantage of the low draw. One of the leading chances. EBONY IDOL (5) had the drop on the lead and went on to be beaten 1.5 lengths into third (20.24) at this track in a Maiden over 350m. Can measure up. ROBELL DONNY (1) is a 19 start maiden who has placed six times, the latest finishing sixth at this track. Reliable out of the boxes and should take advantage of the inside draw. Expected to feature in the finish. SPITFIRE REIGN (2) is by Sunset Spitfire out of Push Me making debut. Gets every chance from the inside draw. Can sneak into the frame at her first appearance.",
